    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 A80 Supra Turbo is a mechanically sound example featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six with its factory sequential twin-turbocharged setup intact. The drivetrain is centered around the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power transfer and traction. The chassis maintains its precision via the original double-wishbone suspension configuration. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul and a compression test confirming all cylinders are within healthy operating parameters. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with its age, the structural and mechanical components remain robust and ready for the track or spirited canyon runs.",
