    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the minor, expected stone chips from highway use that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin featuring supple leather seating and a dashboard free of any cracks or sun damage. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has received consistent synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes were recently serviced to ensure a firm, responsive feel. This is a turn-key vehicle, perfect for someone looking for reliability and comfort without the showroom-new price tag.",
